import { AppBar, Box, Toolbar, Typography } from "@mui/material"

function Navbar() {
    return (
        <>
            <Box>
                <AppBar>
                    <Toolbar>
                        <Typography>Al-Baik</Typography>
                    </Toolbar>
                </AppBar>
            </Box>
        </>
    )
}

export default Navbar
